data.value: Wife to Bill Bourbon. Mrs. Bourbon Reported to investigators that she was upstairs during the time of her husband's murder, and came down stairs when she heard a gun shot. She reports that she saw no one in the crime scene, but overheard her niece Deb U. Taunt asking the Butler where the pistol was kept. Beautrix claims she would never hurt her husband, and says any claims made against her are rediculous.
